text: kraoyomk chaur eng( khmoum) sai nouv real phokophl teanglay ruoch haey chaur eng haohhaer tamophlauv nei mcheasa robsa eng daoy ngeayosruol choh . tuk del chenhpi poh robsa vea mean pnr phe sa ng knea del nowknong noh kuchea aosath pyeabeal samreab mnoussa lok . pitabrakd nasa nowknong rueng noh kuchea phosdo tang muoy samreab mnoussa lok del cheh kitpichearna
